        Existing canonical pattern: subsystem overview → component model → data flow diagrams → file map → cross-references. Match this style.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Maker guide format" location="docs/guides/BUILD-A-NEW-WORKSPACE-WIDGET.md">
