    <criterion testable="true">No SUPERSEDED markers + no broken links + no duplicated content vs existing docs (cross-reference, don't repeat)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Failure modes table in architecture doc covers ≥4 modes (orphan placeholders, missing inputBinding, malformed JSON, output schema violation)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Decision tree in maker guide can route a non-expert maker to "use this pattern" vs "use hardcoded C#" vs "use another AI dispatch" without further consultation</criterion>
